{"tid":583841,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"廢老橫過馬路時不慎「倒街」","createTime":"2018-03-07T10:41:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-07T10:51:41.000Z","uid":75969,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b5ab5f0a9ea1d1bea2558af6d7954248eb6d8dba","tid":583841,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T10:41:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180307/photo/bkn-20180307133740589-0307_00822_001_01p.jpg?20180307135723\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180307%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180307133740589-0307_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20180307135723&h=2ff1397f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n馬路如虎口，無論是途人或司機，均要打醒十二分精神。近日網上有片段指，上水有大叔橫過馬路時仆倒，險遭駛至的車輛輾過，情況驚險！<br />\n<br />\n片段被上載至社交群組「馬路的事討論區」，從片段可見，星期二（6日）晚上近11時，一名大叔在上水新豐路步出馬路，期間疑見等候燈號的車輛開始起動，於是加快步伐跑過，豈料突然兩腳絆倒，仆倒在馬路中心。<br />\n<br />\n其時有車輛駛至，幸司機及時發現，即時煞停車輛始避過一禍。該名大叔急忙起身，向司機揮一揮手致歉，隨即快步離去。<br />\n<br />\n不少網民大呼情況驚險，估計大叔有急事，才會快步衝出馬路，又有人笑言大叔是「賽跑冠軍」，或是屠龍勇者︰「芒亨招緊急迴避」。不過點都好啦，過馬路謹記遵守交通規則，咪貪一時之快。<br />\n<br />\n根據《道路交通（交通管制）規例》，任何人不准在身處距離交通燈控制的過路處15米範圍內，但卻不在該等交通燈所運作的過路處橫過馬路，違者最高可被罰款2,000港元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180307/bkn-20180307133740589-0307_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180307%2Fbkn-20180307133740589-0307_00822_001.html&d=DRiYCPtFnkLeQ%2Ftp453ZXv9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=89fcdd25\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180307/bkn-20180307133740589-0307_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"f4fb10076a9a26b1f6087ccabb74c403bfdf850d","tid":583841,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T10:41:58.000Z","msg":"打錯字<br />\n「仆街」先啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b899f40d9da71e0e9fa2ac59ae1e4db3e5e246e","tid":583841,"uid":22566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T10:42:52.000Z","msg":"倒街啦你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee064893c7ea3a3edad9a97b6b05e18d4e29b38c","tid":583841,"uid":173208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T10:43:25.000Z","msg":"想死都死唔去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d1cae320b07d16097316daafc7d5f6398b15319","tid":583841,"uid":174110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T10:45:35.000Z","msg":"我賽跑冠軍嚟㗎麻<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53b1309ea3a9d7e657d51544e89abcb905be60f3","tid":583841,"uid":164167,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6d1cae320b07d16097316daafc7d5f6398b15319","tid":583841,"uid":174110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T10:45:35.000Z","msg":"我賽跑冠軍嚟㗎麻<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T10:51:41.000Z","msg":"生前"}]}